Plot marker genes across pseudotime

then use a ridge plot to visualize gene expression using package ggridges

loess_gene <- function(gene, cells, count_mtx, ptime_df, n=1000, ...) {
  df <- enframe(count_mtx[cells, gene], name="sample", value="value") %>% 
  left_join(ptime_by_cell, by="sample")
  loess_fit <- loess(value ~ ptime_rank, data = df, ...)
  x_pos <- seq(from=min(df$ptime_rank), to=max(df$ptime_rank), length.out=n)
  out_df <- tibble(ptime_rank = x_pos)
    add_column(out_df, smooth = predict(loess_fit, out_df)) %>% 
    mutate(smooth = (smooth-min(smooth))/(max(smooth)-min(smooth)))
}

ptime_by_cell <- mofa_out %>%
  dplyr::select(sample, ptime_rank)
genes_to_plot <- c("Aqp4", "Slc1a3", "Egfr", "Mki67", "Dcx", "Prokr2", "Rbfox3", "Gria1", "Calb2")
names(genes_to_plot) <- genes_to_plot
genes_to_plot %>%
  map_df(~loess_gene(., lineage_cells, rna_mtx_lognorm, ptime_by_cell, span=.4), .id = "gene") %>% 
  mutate(gene = fct_rev(fct_relevel(gene, genes_to_plot))) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = ptime_rank, y = gene, height = smooth, fill = gene)) +
  geom_density_ridges(stat = "identity", scale = 1.1) + 
  scale_x_continuous(expand = c(0, 0), breaks = NULL) +
  scale_y_discrete(expand = c(0, 0)) +
  coord_cartesian(clip = "off") +
  scale_fill_viridis_d(option="G") +
  theme_ridges(grid = FALSE, center_axis_labels = TRUE) +
  theme(legend.position = "none") +
  labs(x = "cells ordered by pseudotime", y = "") +
  new_scale_color() +
  geom_rug(mapping = aes(x = ptime_rank, y = 0, color = celltype),
           data = distinct(mofa_out, celltype, ptime_rank),
           sides="b", size=1, length=unit(.5, "mm"), inherit.aes=F) +
  scale_color_ct()

Correlating gene expression with meth&acc of variable regions and promoters

Read mappings of variable regions to genes
For each methylation-variable region, we take overlapping or nearest genes.
For each accessibility-variable region, we take the nearest transcription start site.

methvr_gene_overlaps <- read_tsv("/mnt/volume/20-11-03_scNMT-SVZ2/analysis/21-11-10_genes-overlapping-methVRs.tsv.gz", show_col_types=F) %>% 
  group_by(region) %>%
  arrange(dist_tss, gene_id) %>% 
  slice_head(n=1) %>% 
  ungroup()
# methVR -> nearest gene (to gene body)
methvr_to_gene <- methvr_gene_overlaps %>% dplyr::select(region, gene_symbol) %>% deframe()
# gene -> nearest methVR
gene_to_methvr <- methvr_gene_overlaps %>% 
  group_by(gene_symbol) %>%
  arrange(dist_tss, gene_id) %>% 
  slice_head(n=1) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% dplyr::select(gene_symbol, region) %>% deframe()

accvr_tss_dist <- read_tsv("/mnt/volume/20-11-03_scNMT-SVZ2/DNA/07_matrix/GpC_filtered-varRegions_0.02_1000bw_10step_blacklist_closestGenes.bed",
         col_types = "cii--i-c--i",
         col_names = c("chrom", "start", "end", "tss", "gene_id", "dist")) %>% 
  mutate(dist_tss = abs(dist)) %>%
  unite("region", c("chrom", "start", "end"), remove=F) %>% 
  mutate(gene_symbol = gene_id_to_symbol[gene_id])
# accVR -> nearest gene (to TSS)
accvr_to_gene <- accvr_tss_dist %>% dplyr::select(region, gene_symbol) %>% deframe()
# gene -> nearest accVR
gene_to_accvr <- accvr_tss_dist %>% 
  group_by(gene_symbol) %>%
  arrange(abs(dist_tss), gene_id) %>% 
  slice_head(n=1) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% dplyr::select(gene_symbol, region) %>% deframe()

  load_region_gene_mapping <- function(fpath, id2symbol) {
    read_tsv(fpath,
             col_types = "ciid-i-c-ci",
             col_names = c("chrom", "start", "end", "var", "tss", "gene_id", "strand", "dist")) %>% 
      mutate(region_width = end - start) %>% 
      unite("feature", chrom, start, end) %>% 
      mutate(gene_symbol = unname(id2symbol[gene_id])) %>% 
      unite("region_labeled", feature, gene_symbol, remove=F)
  }
  
  cor_test <- function(x, y, ...) {
    if (sum(!is.na(y)) < 3) {
      out <- data.frame(corr = NA, p = NA)
    } else {
      res <- suppressWarnings(cor.test(x, y, ...))
      out <- data.frame(corr = res$estimate, p = res$p.value)
    }
    out
  }
  
  stopifnot(all.equal(rownames(rna_mtx_lognorm), rownames(meth_mtx)))
  stopifnot(all.equal(rownames(rna_mtx_lognorm), rownames(acc_mtx)))
  stopifnot(all.equal(rownames(rna_mtx_lognorm), rownames(meth_mtx_promoter)))
  stopifnot(all.equal(rownames(rna_mtx_lognorm), rownames(acc_mtx_promoter)))

    load_region_gene_mapping(gene_id_to_symbol) %>%
    left_join(enframe(colSums(!is.na(meth_mtx)), name="feature", value="n_obs"), by="feature") %>% 
    dplyr::filter(gene_symbol %in% colnames(rna_mtx_lognorm) & feature %in% colnames(meth_mtx) & n_obs >= 5) %>%
    rowwise() %>%
    mutate(cor_test(rna_mtx_lognorm[, gene_symbol], meth_mtx[, feature], use="pairwise.complete.obs", method="pearson")) %>% 
    ungroup() %>%
    mutate(padj = p.adjust(p, method="fdr")) %>% 
    group_by(gene_symbol) %>% 
    mutate(closest = abs(dist) == min(abs(dist), na.rm=T),
           best = p == suppressWarnings(min(p, na.rm=T))) %>% 
    ungroup()
  
  region_acc_cor <- "/mnt/volume/20-11-03_scNMT-SVZ2/DNA/07_matrix/GpC_filtered-varRegions_0.02_1000bw_10step_blacklist_closestGenes.bed" %>%

as_grange <- function(df, column=feature, center_only=T, ucsc_fmt=F) {
  column <- rlang::enquo(column)
  df <- df %>% 
    dplyr::distinct(!!column) %>%
    tidyr::separate(!!column, into=c("chrom", "start", "end"), convert=T, remove=F) %>% 
    dplyr::select(chrom, start, end, !!column)
  if (center_only) {
    df <- df %>%
      dplyr::mutate(center = round((start + end) / 2)) %>%
      dplyr::select(chrom, start=center, end=center, !!column)
  } else {
    df <- df %>%
      dplyr::select(chrom, start, end, !!column)
  }
  if (ucsc_fmt) {
    df <- df %>% 
      dplyr::mutate(chrom = paste0("chr", chrom)) 
  }
  df %>%
    dplyr::arrange(chrom, as.integer(start)) %>%
    GenomicRanges::GRanges()
}

quantify_overlaps <- function(query_gr, subject_gr, ...) {
  ol <- mergeByOverlaps(
    query = query_gr,
    subject = subject_gr,
    ignore.strand = T,
    ...
  )
  
  n_no_overlap <- length(query_gr) - nrow(ol)
  
  table(ol$type) %>%
    as_tibble(.name_repair = function(x) {c("ccRE", "count")}) %>%
    add_row(ccRE="no overlap", count=n_no_overlap)
}
